Ave K, north side, between Stillwell Ave., and West 11th Street, show ing a new development in this area of Coney Island. To the right, is Hhibbard Creek, and in the background (high chimney) is the City incinerator
for the area.
August 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
